Package com.pom.crimson.testcases.explore.high

Contains Test classes for Testing High priority Explore modules in the mobile app.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasedOnGroupsPageTest
    This test class contains test cases for Based on groups page.
    Based on Groups Page contains articles and videos as per user's joined groups.
    ContentPageTest
    This test class contains test cases for Content page or Full Article page.
    ContentPage or Full Article page displays article content.
    DiscoverTopicsPageTest
    This test class contains test cases for Discover by Interests page.
    Discover by Interests page helps is searching content by user's interest.
    ExplorePageTest
    This test class contains test cases for Explore Page or Content page.
    Explore Page or Content page displays articles and videos as per user's interests and joined groups.
    FilteredInterestResultPageTest
    This test class contains test cases for Filtered Interest Result page.
    Filtered Interest Result Page articles and videos as per specific interest.
    UpdateYourInterestPageTest
    This test class contains test cases for Your preferred interests page.
    AddMoreInterestPage or Your preferred interests page can be used to add more interests to profile.
